title: Expenses and benefits: offshore transfers in the oil and gas industries

heading_context: Expenses and benefits: offshore transfers in the oil and gas industries
chunks.html_content: As an employer in the oil and gas sector, you regularly cover the expense of transporting employees between the mainland and their permanent workplace on an offshore rig or similar installation.
chunks.plain_content:
Expenses and benefits: offshore transfers in the oil and gas industries
As an employer in the oil and gas sector, you regularly cover the expense of transporting employees between the mainland and their permanent workplace on an offshore rig or similar installation.

heading_context: Expenses and benefits: offshore transfers in the oil and gas industries
chunks.html_content: You don’t need to report these expenses to HMRC or to pay tax or National Insurance on them.
chunks.plain_content:
Expenses and benefits: offshore transfers in the oil and gas industries
What to report and pay
You don’t need to report these expenses to HMRC or to pay tax or National Insurance on them.
